These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, oliveros, blend, tiparillo
4 different games are played: go, poker, backgammon, chess
1. the person playing chess is not to the right of the person playing go##8
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
4. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
5. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
7. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere between the siglo-smoker and the person playing poker##7
8. the oliveros-smoker and the person playing chess have the same parity positions##9
9. the blend-smoker and the person playing go have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | siglo | oliveros | blend     | tiparillo |
| Pet           | backgammon   | chess     | poker | go  |

