.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, turkish, colombian, british
City: san-francisco, berlin, liverpool, hamburg
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to hamburg and the turkish have the same parity positions##9
3. the person traveling to berlin is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the right of the british##8
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
6. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
7. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
8. the british is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | british     | colombian    | thai | turkish    |
| Hobby      | san-francisco | berlin | liverpool      | hamburg |

