.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, daffodil, begonia, daisy
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, orange, white, lavender
1. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
2. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person who likes ivory is not to the left of the person who likes orange##8
8. the person who growsdaffodil and the person who likes orange have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | daffodil    | begonia   | orchid    | daisy  |
| Food       | orange | lavender | ivory | white |

