.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, farmhouse, victorian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, august, may, june
1. the person who's birthday is in november is the gothic-revival house##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the art-deco house##1
6. the victorian house and the person who's birthday is in june have the same parity positions##9
7. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | victorian | farmhouse | art-deco  | gothic-revival |
| Music-Genre   | may             | august          | june | november    |

