.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, white, turquise, coral
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, mirinda, soy-milk
1. the person who likes turquise is not the person drinking mirinda##6
2. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who likes lavender have different parity positions##9
3. the person drinking cola and the person who likes white have different parity positions##9
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
6. the person who likes white is not the person drinking cola##6
7. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
9. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person who likes coral##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | lavender | turquise | coral  | white |
| Pet           | cola   | iced-tea     | mirinda | soy-milk      |

