2. the person who's sport is sailing and the fan hip-hop have the same parity positions##9
3. the fan disco is somewhere to the right of the fan rock##5
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the fan disco##3
5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the fan disco and the fan hip-hop##7
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | golf | volleyball   | baseball | sailing |
| Transport   | rock   | disco | gospel    | hip-hop      |

