.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, airplane, bike
4 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, horse, rabbit
 1. the person driving the ship and the owner of the horse have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
 3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the helicopter##7
 4. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
 5. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
 6. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
 7. the person driving the bike and the owner of the frog have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 9. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
10. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | helicopter  | bike | airplane  | ship |
| Music-Genre   | rabbit | horse     | ferret | frog     |

