.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-18::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, lettuce, pomegranate, plum
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, subway, jet-ski, van
1. the person eating plum and the person driving the tram have the same parity positions##9
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
4. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating lettuce##8
5. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the jet-ski and the person eating pear have the same parity positions##9
7. the person driving the tram and the person eating pomegranate have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | pear | plum | lettuce | pomegranate |
| Pet   | jet-ski    | subway   | van        | tram            |

