.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, daisy, dahlia, rose
4 different pets are kept: bird, turtle, frog, lizard
 1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 4. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
 5. the owner of the bird is not the person who growsdaisy##6
 6. the person who growsrose is not to the right of the person who growsorchid##8
 7. the person who growsrose and the owner of the turtle have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person who growsdahlia##8
 9. the person who growsrose is the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who growsdaisy and the owner of the turtle have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | daisy    | dahlia        | rose   | orchid      |
| Hobby      | lizard | frog | turtle | bird |

 